recommend check-in -- the keystone is named and prioritized on the roadmap, with a composition path and first laps ready; the one thing it waits on is Keaton's word to open P0. That word is the real gate: once given, the next build sitting can host the closed Open Ask loop under a minimal Pool over Caravan's capability table and witness it, exactly as the Neth ladder's laps were witnessed this same day.
